{"tid":1924100,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"龍運巴士三月十五日起在七條路線試行新電子支付系統，支援感應式支付及二維碼支付","createTime":"2020-03-13T12:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T10:51:49.000Z","uid":44569,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"bf5a11dc70f6491b13da4cca51f012fe200b6826","tid":1924100,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"1. 上車前預先準備電子支付工具，例如拿出信用卡或啟動流動支付二維碼 (「QR Code」)。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lwb.hk/chi/images/lwb_epayment/step1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lwb.hk%2Fchi%2Fimages%2Flwb_epayment%2Fstep1.png&h=5e50d2fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 電子支付收費器設於八達通收費器左邊近車門位置；收費器預設為成人票價，小童或長者如需享用半價優惠，請按收費器右上角的按鈕。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lwb.hk/chi/images/lwb_epayment/step2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lwb.hk%2Fchi%2Fimages%2Flwb_epayment%2Fstep2.png&h=d0dfd51f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 在收費器下方位置拍信用卡，進行付款。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lwb.hk/chi/images/lwb_epayment/step3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lwb.hk%2Fchi%2Fimages%2Flwb_epayment%2Fstep3.png&h=1c75d581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者在收費器上方鏡頭掃描二維碼，進行付款。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lwb.hk/chi/images/lwb_epayment/step4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lwb.hk%2Fchi%2Fimages%2Flwb_epayment%2Fstep4.png&h=16b0dc98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 收費器發出提示聲並顯示「歡迎乘搭」，代表交易完成。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lwb.hk/chi/images/lwb_epayment/step5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lwb.hk%2Fchi%2Fimages%2Flwb_epayment%2Fstep5.png&h=da1adc06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n*注意：如欲用同一張卡或同一個帳戶替多於一位乘客付款，每次交易之間須相隔五分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.lwb.hk/tc/lwb-epayment.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lwb.hk%2Ftc%2Flwb-epayment.html&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=94c1be08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.lwb.hk/tc/lwb-epayment.html</a>"},{"pid":"689ca3cddef818e3e421ef8115c0844d97f188b3","tid":1924100,"uid":197640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bf5a11dc70f6491b13da4cca51f012fe200b6826","tid":1924100,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"1. 上車前預先準備電子支付工具，例如拿出信用卡或啟動流動支付二維碼 (「QR Code」)。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lwb.hk/chi/images/lwb_epayment/step1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lwb.hk%2Fchi%2Fimages%2Flwb_epayment%2Fstep1.png&h=5e50d2fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 電子支付收費器設於八達通收費器左邊近車門位置；收費器預設為成人票價，小童或長者如需享用半價優惠，請按收費器右上角的按鈕。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lwb.hk/chi/images/lwb_epayment/step2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lwb.hk%2Fchi%2Fimages%2Flwb_epayment%2Fstep2.png&h=d0dfd51f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 在收費器下方位置拍信用卡，進行付款。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lwb.hk/chi/images/lwb_epayment/step3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lwb.hk%2Fchi%2Fimages%2Flwb_epayment%2Fstep3.png&h=1c75d581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者在收費器上方鏡頭掃描二維碼，進行付款。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lwb.hk/chi/images/lwb_epayment/step4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lwb.hk%2Fchi%2Fimages%2Flwb_epayment%2Fstep4.png&h=16b0dc98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 收費器發出提示聲並顯示「歡迎乘搭」，代表交易完成。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lwb.hk/chi/images/lwb_epayment/step5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lwb.hk%2Fchi%2Fimages%2Flwb_epayment%2Fstep5.png&h=da1adc06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n*注意：如欲用同一張卡或同一個帳戶替多於一位乘客付款，每次交易之間須相隔五分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.lwb.hk/tc/lwb-epayment.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lwb.hk%2Ftc%2Flwb-epayment.html&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=94c1be08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.lwb.hk/tc/lwb-epayment.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"re